---
import { IMAGES } from '../config';
---

<section id="que-vas-a-hacer" class="relative">
  <!-- Parallax divider -->
  <div class="parallax-bg h-64 md:h-80" style={`background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(59,36,23,0.5), rgba(59,36,23,0.5)), url('${IMAGES.queVasAHacer}');`}></div>

  <div class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="fade-in">
        <h2 class="section-title text-marron">
          <span class="i18n-es">Qué vas a hacer</span>
          <span class="i18n-en">What you'll do</span>
        </h2>

        <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-arepa mx-auto mb-12 rounded-full"></div>

        <ul class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-arepa/10 text-arepa rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">1</span>
            <p class="text-lg text-marron-light pt-1">
              <span class="i18n-es">Conocer los ingredientes y preparar la masa desde cero</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Get to know the ingredients and prepare the dough from scratch</span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-arepa/10 text-arepa rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">2</span>
            <p class="text-lg text-marron-light pt-1">
              <span class="i18n-es">Formar y cocinar tus propias arepas</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Shape and cook your own arepas</span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-arepa/10 text-arepa rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">3</span>
            <p class="text-lg text-marron-light pt-1">
              <span class="i18n-es">Aprender tips simples para que queden perfectas</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Learn simple tips to make them perfect</span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-arepa/10 text-arepa rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">4</span>
            <p class="text-lg text-marron-light pt-1">
              <span class="i18n-es">Armar y degustar arepas con distintos rellenos preparados previamente para que el foco esté en cocinar y disfrutar</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Assemble and taste arepas with different fillings prepared in advance so the focus is on cooking and enjoying</span>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-arepa/10 text-arepa rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">5</span>
            <p class="text-lg text-marron-light pt-1">
              <span class="i18n-es">Disfrutar la experiencia compartiendo en grupo</span>
              <span class="i18n-en">Enjoy the experience sharing with the group</span>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
